title: Diamond Toplane Searching For A Team (Ranked 5's)
body:
Hey Guys,
I am searching for a Ranked 5's Team to play with!
Elo: Diamond 5
Age: 21
Gender: Male
Server: EUW
AccountName: Master Yirelia
Languages: German & English
Training Schedule: 6 P.M. - midnight (18-24)
What I can bring into the Team:
Years of League Experience
Good Toplaning (as Maokai, Irelia, Gnar, Jax, Master Yi, Quinn, Galio, Malphite, Lissandra, Nasus, Renekton, Trundle, Wukong, Yorick, Darius, ChoGath)
Good Jungling (as Master Yi, Volibear, Maokai, Sejuani, Malphite, Warwick, Amumu, Nocturne, Xin Zhao)
What I want:
Since I went to Diamond, my SoloQ-Goal is reached. I want to play Ranked 5's now, to keep my form and may preparing my way to the esports scene (if I can get there :P)
I'd like to have a team, where I can practice and perform as a Toplaner OR Jungler. Im interested in forging a team bond and winning games with a team.

Strengths:
-Years of Experience
-Owning every Champion
-Ad-Bruisers
-Fulltanks
-Teamcomp-picks by sacrificing own lane-dominance
-Map-Awareness
-strong farming 

Weaknesses:
-lack of Performance at Ap-Carries (Lissandra and Cho'Gath excluded)
-not so much Skins (xD)


If any nescessary Details are missing, post below what you want to know.
